    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Manuscript specimens of Persian songs, writing, illustrations and illuminations by different artists, mounted in a scrapbook.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="530" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
